Tuesday, December 19, 1995

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-2762. Bielefeld v. State Farm Mut. Ins. Co.

Cuyahoga County, No. 67093. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal, i

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective December 18, 1995. j

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed. J
